text: Stenoglene basquini is a moth in the family Eupterotidae. It was described by Thierry Bouyer in 2012. It is found in the Central African Republic., 2012: Description de nouveaux Eupterotidae africains (Lepidoptera). Entomologia Africana. 17 (2): 2-14. ==References== Category:Moths described in 2012 Category:Janinae
